      "span_text": "Recently, a new subcutaneous ICD (S-ICD) was introduced in Europe.  The S-ICD is unique in that its implantation is entirely subcutaneous, eliminating the need for lead placement in or on the heart and simplifying the implant procedure by using anatomical landmarks instead of fluoroscopy imaging."
